/** @format */

import React from 'react';
import {
  Box,
  Card,
  CardActions,
  CardContent,
  Button,
  Typography,
  Paper,
} from '@mui/material';

const Cards = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Box
        omponent="span"
        sx={{ display: 'inline-block', mx: '2px', transform: 'scale(0.8)' }}
      >
        <Card sx={{ minWidth: 275 }}>
          <CardContent>
            <Typography
              sx={{ fontSize: 14 }}
              color="text.secondary"
              gutterBottom
            >
              Balance
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
              $23,345
            </Typography>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Box>
      <Box omponent="span" sx={{ display: 'inline-block', mx: '2px' }}>
        <Card sx={{ minWidth: 275 }}>
          <CardContent>
            <Typography
              sx={{ fontSize: 14 }}
              color="text.secondary"
              gutterBottom
            >
              Payment Due
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h3" component="h4">
              $12,345
            </Typography>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Box>
    </>
  );
};

export default Cards;
